# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Report and any report-like component — kept private, never shared.
# The full written report, its Markdown source, process logs, build scripts,
# and downloaded reference PDFs are all excluded. Only the code and the
# run artifacts (data, figures, outputs) are tracked.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
report/
downloads/
*.docx
*.pdf
